<ab facs="#facs_202_r1l5">vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt / 
